{
  "stem": "1680.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "All day, and the next day Friday afternoon, finally, they took us to the train.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "All the other people went out to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Whatever he didn't like-- they was too old or something.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And Madrich showed up for a few minutes to this appellplatz.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And he saw and talked to [?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Goeth ?] or something and he left, because he probably told him that his people shouldn't be touched.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And Friday afternoon, we went to the train.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "In the train, I had a neighbor.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "He was a dentist, and he had a little boy, and he had a wife and a daughter.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "The wife and daughter went out first day.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "This little boy, he had in a backpack with sleeping pills.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "He was sleeping there for 36 hours.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "Finally, when he came to train, he thought he saved him already.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "So I took him out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And they packed us in 105 people in one car.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And when they took out this little boy, he was-- he didn't know what's going on.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And he gave him an apple to eat.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And he started eating the apple.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, the Gestapo-- the SS came in.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And they pushed everybody in one side from the car.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And one by one, we have to go through until he find this little boy.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And the people were so anxious to get-- to sit down, to relax a little, so they started pushing him.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "So this little boy says, don't push me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "I know I'm gonna die.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And they took out about 30 kids from on the train, because a lot of people-- some of the other people somehow managed to get in the kids.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "And about a block away, we had the shooting.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
